<item>
            <title>[LU-6493] sanity test 42b failure on sync</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6493</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For ticket &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6319&quot; title=&quot;Re-enable tests on ALWAYS_EXCEPT list from Bugzilla&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6319&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6319&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, we&#8217;re running tests that are on the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list to see which ones are still failing and which ones pass. Sanity test 42b has been on the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list for several years now and is failing with error&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;test_42b() &quot;test destroy of file with cached dirty data&quot;
sanity test_42b: @@@@@@ FAIL: 78 &amp;lt; 79 on sync 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test results and logs are at &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7a914250-e8a1-11e4-b3c6-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7a914250-e8a1-11e4-b3c6-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt; . &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This failure is related to the Bugzilla ticket 9789 at &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=9789&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=9789&lt;/a&gt; . If this test is no longer valid, we should remove it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
